line_1: Nor on me thy woes entail.
Thy treasures on this mansion didst entail,
line_2: Thine orphan babes partook a scanty meal.

line_1: What Men have purchas'd, they of Right entail.
line_2: And Fame, conferr'd by you, can never fail:

line_1: And this will cut off the Entail;
line_2: At their true Benefactors to Rail;
